# Global ACL applied to every mailbox. Mailbox owners get exactly:
#   lookup      — mailbox visible in LIST
#   read        — SELECT/FETCH
#   write-seen  — persist \Seen flag in Dovecot's per-user index
# No insert/expunge/write — all other flag changes and APPEND/COPY are rejected. Apple Mail
# silently tolerates this for a read-only account.

* owner lookup read write-seen
